Area of a Rectangle
Create a function that calculates the area of a rectangle. If the arguments are invalid, your function must return -1.

Examples
area(3, 4) ➞ 12

area(10, 11) ➞ 110

area(-1, 5) ➞ -1

area(0, 2) ➞ -1

https://edabit.com/challenge/g6b9HqkXqWu6GpfTo

My Solution

function area(h, w) {
	if (h <= 0 || w <= 0) {
		return -1
	} else return h * w
}
